<section id="content"><div class="breadcrumbs-heading"><div class="bottom"><div class="container"><div class="row"><div class="col-xs-12"><h1 class="semi-bold">Card Payment Services</h1></div></div></div></div><div class="top"><div class="container"><div class="row"><div class="col-xs-12"><ul class="list-inline list-unstyled" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/BreadcrumbList"><li itemprop="itemListElement" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/ListItem"><a itemprop="item" href="https://www.heritageps.net/" title="Home"><span itemprop="name">Home</span><meta itemprop="position" content="1"/></a></li><li itemprop="itemListElement" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/ListItem" class="active"><span itemprop="name">Card Payment Services</span><meta itemprop="position" content="2"/></li></ol></div></div></div></div></div><article class="content-page section-sm"><div class="container"><div class="row services-icons"><div class="col-xs-6 col-sm"><img src="https://www.heritageps.net/content/uploads/media/services/247-support-icon.png" alt="24/7 Support"/> <span class="h3 semi-bold">24/7 US<br/> Based Support</span></div><div class="col-xs-6 col-sm"><img src="https://www.heritageps.net/content/uploads/media/services/business-insights-icon.png" alt="Business Insights"/> <span class="h3 semi-bold">Business<br/> Insights</span></div><div class="col-xs-6 col-sm"><img src="https://www.heritageps.net/content//uploads/media/services/online-reporting-icon.png" alt="Online Reporting"/> <span class="h3 semi-bold">Online<br/> Reporting</span></div><div class="col-xs-6 col-sm"><img src="https://www.heritageps.net/content//uploads/media/services/local-agent-icon.png" alt="Local Agent"/> <span class="h3 semi-bold">Local Agent Representatives</span></div><div class="col-xs-12 col-sm"><img src="https://www.heritageps.net/content//uploads/media/services/software-integrations-icon.png" alt="Software Integrations"/> <span class="h3 semi-bold">Software<br/> Integrations</span></div></div><p>&nbsp;</p><div class="row"><div class="col-xs-12 col-md-7 col-lg-6"><h2>Payment Systems For Every Business</h2><p>Brick-and-mortar or online-only, you want the ability to close every sale quickly and effectively. With several card payment service options to choose from, Heritage Payment Solutions allows for every sale to be a success.</p><ul><li>Card payments improve cash flow with quick deposits.</li><li>Consumers enjoy convenience online and in-person.</li><li>Reduce risk of fraud with automatic transaction screening.</li><li>Allows businesses to stay competitive in any industry.</li></ul><a class="btn btn-primary green" href="https://www.heritageps.net/contact/">Get Started Now</a></div><div class="hidden-xs hidden-sm col-md-5 col-lg-6"><img src="https://www.heritageps.net/content/uploads/media/new-images/lady.jpg" alt="Payment Solutions"/></div></div><div class="row"><div class="col-xs-12"><ul class="nav tabs-nav"><li class="strategy active"><a href="#strategy" data-target="#strategy" data-toggle="tab">Card</a></li><li class="banks"><a href="#banks" data-target="#banks" data-toggle="tab">Check</a></li><li class="careers"><a href="#careers" data-target="#careers" data-toggle="tab">Software</a></li></ul><div class="tab-content"><div id="strategy" class="tab-pane fade in active"><h2>Debit, Credit, EBT - Card Services</h2><p>Card acceptance is a necessity for businesses operating in our technology centric marketplace. It means you can offer convenience to your customers while also securing current and future sales. Credit and debit acceptance makes up for the majority of payments processed in the United States while EBT enables customers the flexibility to utilize benefits at a broad range of businesses. Keep up with industry changes with Heritage Payment Solutions Card acceptance product offerings.</p><a class="btn btn-primary blue" href="https://www.heritageps.net/contact/">Contact Us</a></div><div id="banks" class="tab-pane fade"><h2>Verification Guarantee RDC - Check Services</h2><p>While the industry is making a shift towards electronic payments there are still those businesses that have a crucial need for paper check transactions. Our line of check services gives you the option of everything from a simple verification of funds to full-fledged check conversion with guarantee. We also offer remote deposit capture solutions for businesses to businesses merchants to make it easier to handle large batch check approvals.</p><a class="btn btn-secondary blue" href="https://www.heritageps.net/contact/">Get Started</a></div><div id="careers" class="tab-pane fade"><h2>eCommerce Mobile POS - Software</h2><p>The future is here and as the merchant services industry is taking hold of emerging technologies there is no better time than now to make the switch. Speed, security, portability and many other features of software point of sales make them a formidable contender for the primary means of payment acceptance. Many mobile options operate off of cellular towers and software based systems can use broadband internet to provide "constant on" network connectivity without the hassle of costly analog phone lines; while mobile point of sale systems can utilize existing cell phone plans. We offer competitive, fairly priced gateway options and equipment.</p><a class="btn btn-primary green" href="https://www.heritageps.net/contact/">Request Details</a></div></div></div></div><div class="row"><div class="col-xs-12"><h2>Up-To-Date Security Measures, Reliable Live Support</h2></div><div class="col-sm-6"><ul><li><strong>Support</strong> Have you seen your merchant services account representative lately? At Heritage Payment Solutions, we champion small &amp; medium business. Doing so provides us with the means to provide consistent and meaningful follow ups with our existing merchants. A commitment from you to us is a commitment from us to you.</li></ul></div><div class="col-sm-6"><ul><li><strong>Security</strong> All of our merchants can rest assured that they are processing payments utilizing fully PCI DSS compliant networks and terminal equipment/software. Through our strategic partnership we offer all merchants yearly compliance assessments to assure your business is protected from costly breach fees.</li></ul></div><div class="col-xs-12"><blockquote><p>"Our 24/7 customer service is here to answer immediate questions and concerns, and escalations are handled by our sales representatives so that your business stays running smooth. "</p></blockquote></div></div><div class="row"><div class="col-xs-12"><h3>The Payment Options You &amp; Your Customers Want</h3></div><div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6"><p>Whatever the business or industry you&rsquo;re in, such as foodservice, hospitality, and retail, customers expect multiple payment options. By and large, this means accepting debit and credit cards. Heritage Payment Solutions helps merchants select the best card machine for their setting and guides them through setting up a merchant account. Our machines include hardwired, wireless, and virtual terminals.</p></div><div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6"><p>Heritage Payment Solutions strives to help our merchants understand everything that goes into accepting card payments, such as how card processing works. By thoroughly explaining your options, you&rsquo;re assured to be set up with the best card payment service for your business. From contacting us to activation, your business will be ready to accept many card types in no time.</p></div></div><div class="row"><div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-4"><h4>Credit Card Services</h4><p>Since their introduction in the 1950s, credit cards have helped millions of businesses expand customer bases and enjoy sustained growth. Heritage Payment Solutions assists merchants in upgrading and maintaining credit card equipment and software as technology and security evolve. Contact us to find out how our credit card services can help grow any business!</p></div><div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-4"><h4>Debit Card Services</h4><p>Debit cards have many benefits to merchants, such as lower processing fees for a business and quicker deposits than credit cards. For online merchants, payments with debit cards are done in real-time. All debit card services offered by Heritage Payment Solutions reduce the hassle associated with collection issues and traditional checks.</p></div><div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-4"><h4>EBT Card Services</h4><p>Electronic benefits transfer (EBT) allow many consumers to use their benefits for a variety of items, including household goods. By offering EBT card services, merchants widen their customer base while understanding local needs. EBT card processing is the same as credit and debit cards.</p></div></div></div></article><div class="testimonials"><div class="container"><div class="row"><div class="col-xs-12"><h3>What Our Clients Say</h3><div class="testimonials-slider"><div class="review"><p>"In this "dog eat dog" world we live in it's nice to know there are still ethical people around!"</p><span>Donna B. Jones - Mama's Table Cafe</span></div><div class="review"><p>"Everyone preaches about supporting local business but not everyone puts their money where their mouth is."</p><span>Joe O'Keefe - Wine 101</span></div><div class="review"><p>"My representative has always been up front with me and I have developed a great deal of respect and trust in him."</p><span>Robert Chianelli - Papa Joe's Smoke Shop</span></div><div class="review"><p>"I've worked with Heritage Payment Solutions for years. I appreciate the friendly face-to-face service. I would highly recommend them!"</p><span>Dr. Daniel Yoakum - Heritage Eye Care</span></div><div class="review"><p>"You go way above and beyond the service one would expect from a credit card processing company."</p><span>Warren Mullins - The Bed Zone</span></div></div></div></div></div></div>	<div class="contact-common"><div class="container"><div class="row"><div class="col-xs-12"><h2 class="h1 semi-bold" style="margin-bottom:4rem;">Get In Touch With Us &amp; Keep Your Business Running Smooth</h2></div><div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-4"><img src="/content/uploads/media/new-images/support.png" alt="Support"/><span class="heading">Support</span><p>24/7 Customer Service &amp; Technical Support For <span class="bold">Existing</span> Merchants</p><a title="Call Heritage Payment Solutions" href="tel:8007898897"><span>(800) 789-8897</span></a></div><div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-4"><div class="borders"><img src="/content/uploads/media/new-images/sales.png" alt="Sales"/><span class="heading">Sales</span><a title="Call Heritage Payment Solutions" href="tel:9194531204"><span>Phone: (919) 453-1204</span></a><a title="Fax Heritage Payment Solutions" href="tel:8884547069"><span>Fax: 888-454-7069</span></a><a title="Email Heritage Payment Solutions" href="mailto:danielle.s@heritageps.net"><span>Email: danielle.s@heritageps.net</span></a></div></div><div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-4"><img src="/content/uploads/media/new-images/address.png" alt="Address"/><span class="heading">Address</span><p>616 Dr. Calvin Jones Hwy. Suite 100<br>Wake Forest, NC 27587</p><a href="https://goo.gl/maps/9R1XTcu5PXs" title="Get Directions" target="_blank"><span>View the Map</span></a></div></div></div></div></section><?php include $_SERVER["DOCUMENT_ROOT"] . "/includes/footer.php"; ?>